    1 $accept: compilation_unit EOF

    2 compilation_unit: source_elements

    3 source_elements: /* empty */
    4                | source_elements source_element

    5 source_element: statement
    6               | function_declaration

    7 function_declaration: "function" identifier '(' ')' '{' 
                                source_elements '}'
    8                     | "function" identifier '(' formal_parameter_list 
                                ')' '{' source_elements '}'

    9 formal_parameter_list: identifier
   10                      | formal_parameter_list ',' identifier

   11 statement: empty_statement
   12          | block_statement
   13          | break_statement
   14          | continue_statement
   15          | return_statement
   16          | debugger_statement
   17          | loop_statement
   18          | expression_statement
   19          | switch_statement
   20          | if_statement
   21          | throw_statement
   22          | try_statement
   23          | var_statement
   24          | with_statement
   25          | label_statement

   26 empty_statement: ';'

   27 block_statement: '{' statement_list '}'

   28 statement_list: /* empty */
   29               | statement_list statement

   30 break_statement: "break" ';'
   31                | "break" identifier ';'

   32 continue_statement: "continue" ';'
   33                   | "continue" identifier ';'

   34 return_statement: "return" ';'
   35                 | "return" expression ';'

   36 debugger_statement: "debugger" ';'

   37 loop_statement: do_while_statement
   38               | while_statement
   39               | for_statement

   40 do_while_statement: "do" statement "while" '(' expression ')' ';'

   41 while_statement: "while" '(' expression ')' statement

   42 for_statement: "for" '(' lhs_expression "in" expression ')' statement
   43              | "for" '(' var_fragment_noin "in" expression ')' 
                         statement
   44              | "for" '(' var_fragment_noin ';' opt_expression ';' 
                         opt_expression ')' statement
   45              | "for" '(' expression_noin ';' opt_expression ';' 
                         opt_expression ')' statement
   46              | "for" '(' ';' opt_expression ';' opt_expression ')' 
                         statement

   47 expression_statement: expression_st ';'

   48 switch_statement: "switch" '(' expression ')' '{' switch_body '}'

   49 switch_body: /* empty */
   50            | switch_body switch_case

   51 switch_case: "case" expression ':' statement_list
   52            | "default" ':' statement_list

   53 if_statement: "if" '(' expression ')' statement
   54             | "if" '(' expression ')' statement "else" statement

   55 throw_statement: "throw" expression ';'

   56 try_statement: "try" block_statement "case" '(' identifier ')' 
                         block_statement
   57              | "try" block_statement "finally" block_statement
   58              | "try" block_statement "case" '(' identifier ')' 
                         block_statement "finally" block_statement

   59 var_statement: var_fragment ';'

   60 var_fragment: "var" var_identifier_list

   61 var_fragment_noin: "var" var_identifier_list_noin

   62 var_identifier_list: var_identifier
   63                    | var_identifier_list ',' var_identifier

   64 var_identifier_list_noin: var_identifier_noin
   65                         | var_identifier_list_noin ',' 
                                    var_identifier_noin

   66 var_identifier: identifier
   67               | identifier '=' assignment_expression

   68 var_identifier_noin: identifier
   69                    | identifier '=' assignment_expression_noin

   70 with_statement: "with" '(' expression ')' statement

   71 label_statement: identifier ':' statement

   72 primary_expression: "this"
   73                   | identifier
   74                   | literal
   75                   | array_literal
   76                   | object_literal
   77                   | '(' expression ')'

   78 primary_expression_st: "this"
   79                      | identifier
   80                      | literal
   81                      | array_literal
   82                      | '(' expression ')'

   83 literal: StringLiteral
   84        | NumericLiteral
   85        | "true"
   86        | "false"
   87        | "null"
   88        | '/'
   89        | "/="

   90 array_literal: '[' opt_comma_list ']'
   91              | '[' element_list ']'
   92              | '[' element_list ',' opt_comma_list ']'

   93 element_list: opt_comma_list assignment_expression
   94             | element_list ',' opt_comma_list assignment_expression

   95 comma_list: ','
   96           | comma_list ','

   97 opt_comma_list: /* empty */
   98               | comma_list

   99 object_literal: '{' '}'
  100               | '{' name_value_list '}'
  101               | '{' name_value_list ',' '}'

  102 name_value_list: property_assignment
  103                | name_value_list ',' property_assignment

  104 property_assignment: property_name ':' assignment_expression
  105                    | "get" ':' assignment_expression
  106                    | "set" ':' assignment_expression
  107                    | "get" property_name '(' ')' '{' source_elements 
                               '}'
  108                    | "set" property_name '(' identifier ')' '{' 
                               source_elements '}'

  109 property_name: Identifier
  110              | StringLiteral
  111              | NumericLiteral

  112 member_expression: primary_expression
  113                  | function_expression
  114                  | member_expression '[' expression ']'
  115                  | member_expression '.' identifier
  116                  | "new" member_expression arguments

  119                     | member_expression_st '.' identifier
